These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
House: tower, art-deco, craftsman, victorian, ranch-style
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite, 7up, tea, water
1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the victorian house##1
2. the ranch-style house is on the right of the tower house##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the art-deco house is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
6. the tower house is in the middle##1
7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| House   | art-deco | craftsman | tower | ranch-style | victorian |
| Beverage   | water    | almond-milk | 7up     | tea       | sprite  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
5 different games are played: go, canasta, chess, whist, mah-jongg
City: hamburg, prague, new-york, marseilles, nizza
1. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person playing go is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
3. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing chess##1
4. the person playing go is in the middle##1
5. the person playing canasta is the person traveling to new-york##1
6. the person traveling to nizza is the person playing mah-jongg##1
7. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Game      | canasta | chess | go | whist | mah-jongg |
| City   | new-york  | marseilles   | hamburg       | prague    | nizza   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: d&b, soul, classical, dubstep, r&b
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, aconite, amaryllis, begonia, orchid
1. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
6. the fan of soul is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Music-Genre        | classical | dubstep | soul | d&b | r&b |
| Flower   | aconite  | azalea      | orchid | amaryllis | begonia      |

