.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: green, apricot, lavender, white, aquamarine
5 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker, scrabble, monopoly, billiard
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person playing poker##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
6. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
7. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Color   | white    | green        | lavender | apricot | aquamarine |
| Game     | mah-jongg | monopoly | billiard  | poker   | scrabble |

