.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
There are 5 different nationalities: dutch, thai, french, british, american
There are 5 different favourite colors: black, red, aquamarine, coral, purple
1. the person who likes coral is on the right of the french##1
2. the person who likes red is the american##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the british##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is in the middle##1
5. the french is on the left of the dutch##1
6. the person who likes purple is the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Nationality    | french   | dutch     | thai   | british         | american |
| Color   | black | coral | aquamarine | purple | red     |

