.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: drawing, traveling, singing, photography, gardening
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: zombie, crime, musical, superhero, mystery
1. the person watching superhero movies is in the middle##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person watching musical movies is the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Hobby       | photography   | singing   | traveling | gardening | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | musical | superhero   | mystery | zombie       |

