.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, doctor, electrician, pilot, journalist
There are 5 different nationalities: colombian, argentine, american, chinese, malaysian
1. the electrician is on the right of the chinese##1
2. the colombian is the dancer##1
3. the journalist is on the right of the american##1
4. the dancer is on the left of the pilot##1
5. the argentine is in the middle##1
6. the american is the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Job     | doctor   | electrician  | journalist      | dancer | pilot     |
| Nationality   | chinese | american | argentine | colombian   | malaysian |

