.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: reggae, indie, metal, soul, rock
5 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly, whist, go, billiard
1. the person playing billiard is on the left of the fan of rock##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing whist##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing go##1
4. the fan of rock is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing whist##1
6. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of indie##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Music-Genre     | indie | reggae       | rock | soul | metal    |
| Game   | go   | billiard | whist  | monopoly     | mah-jongg |

