.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
House: cottage, colonial, victorian, art-deco, palace
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: may, december, january, september, february
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the cottage house##1
2. the victorian house is on the right of the cottage house##1
3. the colonial house is on the far right##1
4. the art-deco house is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the palace house is the person who's birthday is in december##1
7. the art-deco house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| House         | art-deco | cottage | victorian | palace | colonial |
| Birthday   | january       | september   | february         | december   | may   |

