.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: fuchsia, green, pink, apricot, light-blue
There are 5 different favourite beverages: mirinda, 7up, milk, soy-milk, coffee
1. the person who likes green is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking 7up is the person who likes fuchsia##1
4. the person who likes light-blue is the person drinking milk##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
6. the person who likes apricot is in the middle##1
7. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Color   | pink | fuchsia      | apricot | green | light-blue |
| Beverage     | soy-milk  | 7up | mirinda     | coffee     | milk  |

