.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-14::.
City: berlin, colone, boston, paris, marseilles
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, bluemaster, alhambra, baccarat, blend
1. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is in the middle##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
4. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
5. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
6. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| City      | marseilles | boston | berlin      | paris | colone      |
| Cigar   | bluemaster  | baccarat       | bolivar | blend  | alhambra |

