.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-15::.
5 different games are played: domino, backgammon, poker, scrabble, go
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: soccer, climbing, parkour, baseball, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing domino##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person playing poker##1
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |     3      |   4    |    5     |
| Game           | scrabble     | go | domino | poker  | backgammon |
| Sport   | soccer | weightlifting               | climbing     | parkour | baseball |

