.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-18::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, october, march, may, june
There 5 different types of food: kiwi, pineapple, cabbage, carrot, mango
1. the person eating carrot is in the middle##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is the person eating carrot##1
3. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is the person eating mango##1
5. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
6. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
7. the person eating mango is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4      |    5     |
| Birthday   | october   | may  | april | june | march  |
| Food         | kiwi | cabbage | carrot  | mango    | pineapple |

