.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, november, may, january, october
5 different games are played: chess, snooker, mah-jongg, scrabble, whist
1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person playing whist##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Birthday   | october     | may       | february     | november  | january  |
| Game      | scrabble | chess | snooker | whist | mah-jongg |

