.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  designer, social-worker, firefighter, manager, bartender
The people have 5 different hobbies: dancing, writing, traveling, collecting, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is writing is in the middle##1
2. the bartender is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the manager is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the firefighter is on the right of the bartender##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the designer##1
6. the designer is on the right of the firefighter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Job   | social-worker | bartender | firefighter | designer | manager |
| Hobby           | drawing | collecting  | writing    | dancing  | traveling   |

 